    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential exhaustion and a sense of being fundamentally broken/unfit for the world. The assistant responds with empathetic validation that, while attempting to be supportive, increasingly uses metaphors of \"letting go\" and \"stepping out\" of the fight in response to the user's hopelessness.",
